{"per_page":10,"total":5,"current":3,"data":[{"title":"知识产权简单了解","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>知识产权是人类在社会实践中创造的智力劳动成果的专有权利。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/Intellectual-property-right","categories":["Fun"]},{"title":"Flutter基础","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"","link":"2021/06/19/FlutterBase","categories":["ComputerScience","Flutter"]},{"title":"MD5","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p><code>MD5</code>是一种<strong>消息摘要算法</strong>,可以产生出一个哈希值,通常时128位（16<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%BD%8D%E5%85%83%E7%BB%84\" target=\"_blank\">字节</a>）的二进制数(32位16进制数)，用于验证信息传输是否被修改。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>实际上<code>MD5</code>并不能看成一个严格意义上的加密算法，因为<code>md5</code>是没有正规的解密途径的。</p>\n<p><code>MD5</code>通常作为处理请求数据，用来生产<strong>密钥</strong>，作为<strong>数字签名</strong>使用。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/MD5","categories":["ComputerScience"]},{"title":"MarkDown使用","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>Markdown是约翰·格鲁伯发明的轻量级标记语言，方便用易读易写的纯文本格式编写文档，然后转换成有效的XHTML（或者HTML）。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/MarkdownLangure","categories":["Fun"]},{"title":"iOS-组件化","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>当项目越来越复杂的时候，平时的通用方案就不太实用了，这个时候就需要对项目组件化了。 组件化这个东西其实并不复杂，本质上是一种app架构思路。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/IOS_ComponentBased","categories":["ComputerScience","iOS"]},{"title":"计算机网络","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>计算机网络是网络时代的基石，从大型计算机到个人电脑，再到手机，计算机网络已经成为了互联网时代的不可缺少的一部分。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/Network","categories":["ComputerScience"]},{"title":".bash_profile在zsh中生效","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"","link":"2021/06/19/Path_Setting_Bug","categories":["ComputerScience","MAC OS"]},{"title":"CocosCreator Tips","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>在使用Cocos Creator进行游戏开发中，所遇到的一些问题答案和一些小技巧，记录下来。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/CocosCreatorTips","categories":["CocosCreator","ComputerScience","Game"]},{"title":"正则表达式","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>正则表达式(Regular Expression)，是计算机科学的一个概念。正则表达式使用单个字符串来描述、匹配一系列匹配某个句法规则的字符串。在很多文本编辑器里，正则表达式通常被用来检索、替换那些匹配某个模式的文本。</p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/RegularExpression","categories":["ComputerScience","正则表达式"]},{"title":"SQL 小计","date":"2021-06-19T14:09:03.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年6月19日","L":"2021/06/19","MM-DD":"06-19"},"excerpt":"<blockquote>\n<p>SQL是访问和处理关系数据库的计算机标准语言<br>\n<code>SELECT * FROM NoteList</code></p>\n</blockquote>","link":"2021/06/19/SQL_Note","categories":["ComputerScience","SQL"]}]}